            214
        ],
        "page_idx": 18
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "请根据要求完成硬件选型，使用康耐视相机CAM-CIC-5000R-14-G（2592*1944芯片尺寸：5.76*4.29RollingShutter)，工作距离为100mm，FOV为57.6mm*42.9mm，求分别使用多大焦距的定焦镜头和多大倍率的远心镜头？",
        "bbox": [
            25,
            246,
            930,
            307
        ],
        "page_idx": 18
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} f / D = h / H \\\\ f = h / H \\star D = 5.76 / 57.6 \\star 100 = 10mm. \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            23,
            364,
            283,
            425
        ],
        "page_idx": 18
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "放大倍率 $= \\frac{h}{H} = 5.76 / 57.6 = 0.1$ 倍",
        "bbox": [
            25,
            479,
            281,
            512
        ],
        "page_idx": 18
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/55b7475a2d9926127aa5b2ba40419f2dda93d39e4cee7f774efc49fac18b479f.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
